# Natural Language Toolkit: Spearman Rank Correlation classifier
#
# Copyright (C) 2001-2007 NLTK Project
# Author: Sam Huston <shuston@csse.unimelb.edu.au>
#         Steven Bird <sb@csse.unimelb.edu.au>
